-- France, Bouygues near stake deal to prepare GE-Alstom -source
-- By Gilles Guillaume
-- Sat Jun 21, 2014 01:18PM EDT
-- None



PARIS, June 21 (Reuters) - The French government is close to a deal to purchase a 20 percent stake in Alstom <ALSO.PA> from Bouygues <BOUY.PA>, preparing the ground for Alstom's agreed tie-up with General Electric <GE.N>, a source close to the discussions said on Saturday.

